divs: sighting detailsi was on vacation in breckenridge with my family and took photos on dec 6 2007. a few days ago, i was looking at them and noticed something in the photographs. as i zoomed in, it is obvious that i caught an unidentified flying object on film. you have to see these photos. i didn't notice the object at the time i took these photos. the object looks like a bell shape. you can clearly see the bottom of it. in one of the photos you can see a tail or streak following it. you can also see where it went through the white streak\cloud of an airplane. i have not erased the chip that these photos are on. i truly think this is something. i'm not one to fabricate things. i do believe this is something special. i'm not willing to share these photos until i speak with someone directly. thanks!
Summary: I discovered this object in my vacation photos. It's very clear
